Iḥettet akk ayen i d-yeggran
Sazedgen akk iberdan n taddart-nsen
Mkul ass nettat tessefqaɛ-iyi s lehḍuṛ-is
Tettxemmim kan ɣef yiman-is
Ur tessin ara akk ad txemmem ɣef wiyaḍ
Ilaq ad tḥemmleḍ ayen i txeddmeḍ
Win ixeddmen s wul-is yettaweḍ ayen i yettmenni
Win yessaramen ixeddem, ma d win ur nesɛi ara asirem ur ixeddem ara
Win yeṭṭfen deg usirem-is, ḥaca awwaḍ ara yaweḍ ɣuṛ-s
Ma tewwiḍ-d taɣawsa gar wallen-ik, azzel arma teṭṭfeḍ-tt-id!
Iqsed ad yaweḍ lebɣi-s ama ass-a ama azekka
Iguma ad iḥbes asbeɛbeɛ yizimer-nni
Idegdeg deg uḍaṛ
Mkul mi ara d-iɛeddi ɣef uzniq-nneɣ yesčenčin nnaqus-is
Am nnaqus yeṭṭenṭunen neɣ am ṭṭbel yeddendunen
Am win ikkaten ṭṭbel i uɛeẓẓug
Am win iceṭṭḥen i uderɣal
Iḥemmel anadi ussnan
Yesɣaṛay arrac n uɣerbaz amezwaru
Ilha uḥewwes di temdint n Bgayet
Imezdaɣ n Weqqas ttheyyin yiwen n tmeɣṛa telha mliḥ
Imezdaɣ n Ukfadu nnumen asemmiḍ
Imezdaɣ n sseḥra nnumen azɣal
Yeswa snat n litrat n waman
Tisit n waman telha i tezmert
Ur izmir ara ad ixdem aṭas n wussan
Ixeddem tlata n wussam di ssmana
Ixeddem tmanya n sswayeɛ deg wass
Yebɣa ad iṛuḥ ar Fransa ad iɛic dinna
Teɛǧeb-as temɛict di tlemmast n Bgayet
Ur yessin ula d yiwet n taddart deg Tizi-Wezzu
Yebɣa ad d-izzi akk i temdinin n Fransa
Iṭṭef-iten ccambiḍ gezzmen tizmerin deg udrar
Adrar n Ukfadu yeččur d tizantin
Idurar n At Weɣlis sɛan aṭas n ukerruc
Wissen ma yella ad d-yas ass-a ɛli neɣ xaṭi?
Wellah ma ẓṛiɣ ma yella ad d-iṛuḥ neɣ xaṭi
Ur fhimeɣ ara akk amek i yettxemmim wemdan-nni
Ur ḥṣiɣ ara ad ixdem ayen i s-nniɣ
Cukkeɣ tegla s wayen i d-yeǧǧa gma-s
Ur fudeɣ ara akken i lluẓeɣ
Yettlaẓ mi ara d-yeɣli yiḍ
Aqjun-nneɣ d aferḍas am widak-nni n ssyada
Iṣubb ar ssuq ad d-yaɣ tayuga n yezgaren
D azɣal ɣef madden meṛṛa mačči kan fell-aneɣ
Tilawin n At ɛebbas qefzent deg tceɣlatin
Mi ara tleḥḥu, ur tettmil ara zelmeḍ-yeffus
ɣad bbubent arraw-nsent, ur d-ttcetkayent ɣef leɛtab
bɣan qqazen iberdan i wakken ad sɛeddin aman
wwin-d aṭas n tmacicin s ara ɣzen abrid
wwin timacinin akken ad ssun i webrid-nni
d ageffur n tegrest i d-ixedmen akk iremjen-nni deg ubrid
di tmura irebḥen ur tettṛuḥu ara akk trisiti
anda ur isgunfa ara wergaz-a?
acuɣeṛ ur tettnadiḍ ara ansa i ak-d-tekka tyita?
Ini-yi-d mi ara tekkreḍ i wakken ad ṭṭfeɣ amkan-nni!
Sawel-iyi-d azekka ɣef ttnac
Ad nemsawal azekka neɣ seld azekka ɣef setta n tmeddit
Zik nettemyehḍaṛ, ma d tura walu
Tfukk tallit-nni n cceṛ, tura imdanen lhan kan d yiman-nsen
Nwiɣ yettxemmim am yergazen, ziɣen yeččuṛ wul-is d cceṛ
Izmer ad k-iḥsed ula deg iẓẓan
Tenwiḍ ad fehmen yemdanen-a naɣ?
Tenwiḍ akka i ttxemmimen akk madden neɣ?
Seg asmi d-necfa nettat tella da
Seg asmi d-necfa imɣaṛen-nneɣ ttɣaman deg ufrag n taddart
Tibḥirt tuḥwaǧ win ara tt-ineqcen i wakken ad d-tefk lɣella
Tazemmurt yettwaneqcen tettaǧǧa-d aṭas n uzemmur
Yelha ma txedmeḍ-as zzit uzemmur
Yeqqaṛ deg Terga Uzemmur
Yeɣṛa tasenselkimt armi yeɛwej, taggara yebɣa ad ixdem ayen-nniḍen
Yeɣṛa-d di tesdawit n Bgayet, meɛna ixeddem di tesdawit n Tizi-Wezzu
Ddu d uḍar-ik a mmi-s n tmurt !
Win iḥemmlen isekla, issen amek ara ten-yefres
Igran weṛṛaɣit, ihi d lawan n uḥuccu
Imenna-d ad yečč asunedwič
Yesfaqed ma mazal llan deg umkan-nni neɣ ṛuḥen
Kra n tedyanin n zik
Mi ara d-megren, ttaǧǧan amur n uẓawali
Ass n lexmis taṣebḥit
Ass n ssebt tameddit
Ass n lḥedd ɣef ttnac n uzal
Rzan ar tferkiwin-nsen ad ten-neqcen
Ad d-kksen tibexsisin akked tṛemmanin
Ad d-kksen irden akked temẓin
Bdu-d seg iri arma d wayeḍ ahat ad d-ibin kra
Ula d iɣersiwen ttmeslayen way-gar-asen
Izux ɣef madden s wayen ur nelli d ayla-s
Ulac win ara yezwin azemmur alamma serḥen yemɣaṛen n taddart
Ulac win yellan deg ubrid ɣef ttnac n uzal
Sarameɣ kan ad yi-d-qeblen asuter-inu
Ifqeɛ fell-as aṭas i mi mačči d netta i s-yennan 
Ur ibɣi ara ad as-ceyyɛen yiwen-nniḍen ara s-iɛawden i ccɣel-nni
Ur iban ara akk ma d netta neɣ d nettat i yettwaqeblen
Yal tikkelt ara sɛelmeɣ yiwen ur ttawḍeɣ ara ayen i bɣiɣ
Uɣalen xeddmeɣ lecɣal-iw mebla ma yeɛlem yiwen
Qqimeɣ kan gar-asen ttmuqquleɣ s wallen-iw
Nettat tetteffer akk ticeɣlatin-is, d nkenti kan i d nniyat nḥekku-yas kullec
Nessaram ad nernu tutlayt taqbaylit ar Google
Gguleɣ ma teqqel akk ad tsel s wayen i xeddmeɣ neɣ anda i rriɣ
Win yettgalan s waṭas yeskidib
Nekk uɣaleɣ ur ttamneɣ ara akk widak i yettẓalan axaṭer d at sin wudmawen
Ur yi-ttlummu ara ma yella ur d-usiɣ ara axaṭer ttwaṭṭfeɣ s waṭas n lecɣal
Yeqqim rrif n wassif ikkat tibyirin ɣef yiman-is
Tebɣa ad yi-tt-teḥcu akken ttmuqquleɣ s wallen-iw
Tebɣa ad yi-tenheṛ am izimer, ad xedmeɣ ayen i yi-d-teqqaṛ
Ut ttaɣeɣ awal i yiwen, xeddmeɣ kan ayen i yi-d-yenna uqeṛṛuy-iw
Ur ttakkeɣ ara tameẓẓuɣt i yemdanen am winna, axaṭer si zik netta yettɛassa kan imdanen
Aṭas-aya seg mi i m-d-nniɣ ur s-qqaṛ walu, meɛna kemmi tḥemmleɣ ad tt-tesɛelmeḍ 
Txeddem kullec s tuffra i wakken yiwen ur s-isexṛab lecɣal-is
Asmi ara taf ayen i tuḥwaǧ, imir-nni ad ken-tettu meṛṛa
Ur d-tettmektay ul d yiwen mi ara taweḍ ar wayen tebɣa
ḥrec ihi, tettḥadareḍ iman-ik ɣef izerman-a meṛṛa
yuɣ-d taɣaṭ d uzimer i wakken ad idhu deg teksawt
yettṛebbi itbiren akked tmiṛeqwamin
yeẓẓa tikalitusin i wakken ur ittsax ara yiger-ines
igzem taslent-nni i yeẓẓa baba-s deg tmazirt ufella
izwi-d meṛṛa tizemrin-nni, tura ilaq ad neɛeddi ar ulqaḍ
meyyez mliḥ mliḥ uqbel ad tekkreḍ ar ugennez
ibbuḥra-d lḥal tameddit-a
Wissen anda i lemden warrac-nneɣ tagnizit?
Wissen acuɣeṛ akka i tsetḥa s teqbaylit-is?
Wissen d acu i ilaqen ad t-nawi yid-nneɣ mi ara neffeɣ ar uḥewwes?
Nezmer ad nissin aṭas n tɣawsiwin ma yella nebɣa
Win yebɣan kra, yekkat i wakken ad t-yaweḍ
Iḥemmel ad yurar s tgiṭart-is deg iḍ
Aṭas n tutlayin i ineggren, aṭas-nniḍen i d-ilulen
Tamaziɣt d tawacult n tutlayin, mačči d yiwet n tutlayt
Taqbayit d tutlayt mačči d tantala akken i nenwa zik
Ad d-yeffeɣ wungal-is deg ussan i d-iteddun
Yettaru tiktabin meɛna ur tent-id-isuffuɣ ara
Yečča aṭas meɛna mazal ur yeṛwi ara
Yewweḍ ar wayen i yebɣa meɛna mazal ibɣa ad yuɣal muɛaɛ akter n wannect-a
Seg mi d-yekker netta d učči meɛna mazal ur yeččuṛ ara uɛebbuḍ-is
Adrim i s-d-ikeččmen ibennu yes axxam anda ara yezdeɣ
Bɣan akk yilemẓiyen ad zewǧen meɛna ur sɛin ara ixammen
Fkan-tt tezwzǧ ar Lɛerc n At Menṣuṛ
Deg wayen i yeḥma lḥal, alɣem izmer ad d-ifunzer dinna deg Sedduq
Deg wayen i semmeḍ lḥal, axenziz-ik ad ibedd dinna deg Ukfadu
Tettwaxneq akk temdint-nni, ur tt-id-ikeččem ara akk ubeḥri
Anwa argaz i yeffɣen mi d-yekcem Maziɣ ar tzeqqa-nni?
Anta tamɣaṛt i yeẓṛan belli ilha zzit uzemmur i udeddic
Anwa aqcic ur nezṛi ara belli tutlayt taqbaylit tekcem deg tussna
Nebɣa ad nesɣeṛ tussna s teqbaylit
Amennuɣ s tsertit yeččur d ikeddiben, nekni nebɣa tidett
Ma yella ur d-terri ara tteṛ ur teggan ara
Ur tt-tetteqqed ara arma terra-d tteṛ
D acu i d winna i d-tceyyɣeḍ akken?
Acuɣeṛ i d-tceyyɛeḍ winna?
Ad ak-d-rreɣ s wawal asmi ara yi-d-terreḍ uqble kečči s wawal
Mazal ɛad ur bdint ara tmeɣṛiwin n unebdu
Ur-ɛad bdint tmeɣṛiwin n unebdu
Nettṛaju melmi ara yezweǧ gma-s n Takfarinas ad necḍeḥ
Sbeṛ kan a tamɣaṛt, ur ittɛeṭṭil ara ad d-yelḥeq
Awi-d afus ad am-d-qqneɣ kra n lḥenni
Ur cfiɣ ara akk belli xedmeɣ annect-a
Mi ara yeskeṛ ur iɛellem ara akk d acu i ixeddem
Ttagaden widak yeɣṛan, axaṭer ẓṛan widak ad sen-fiqen belli sbeṛwiḍen kan
ḥemmleɣ ad sleɣ i yefrax sčewčiwen ɣef tzemrin
yufa lɛecc n tsekkurt yeččuṛ d timellalin
ccah axaṭer d kečč i d-yezwaren ar wannect-a
ma yella ur tqudreḍ ara iman-ik, ulac win ara k-iqadṛen
tesɛa lxana ɣef udem-is tettbon-d ar libɛid akya
tenhewwel taddart am urgaz am tmeṭṭut
ffɣen akk yergazen ad berzen igran-nsen uqbel ad d-yaweḍ unebdu
ffɣen akk ar ubraz neɣ mulac ad tsenger kullec tmes n unebdu
ur ɛlimeɣ ara ma yella d tteṛ i bɣiɣ ad d-rreɣ neɣ d acu-t.
Zṛiɣ kan belli yečča-d ul-iw yerna mliḥ akya
Ini-d tura kečči iwacu i txedmeḍ annect-nni, umbaɛed ad ak-d-rreɣ nekki
Wali kemmi tura d acu i txedmeḍ, sienna ad nẓeṛ d acu i texdem nettat
Yiwen ur ittmuqqul ar leɛyub-is netta, ttmuqulen akk ar wiyaḍ
Alɣem yettwali kan taɛrurt-nni n gma-s, ur iwala ara akk tinn-is
ɛni tufiḍ-d anda i terra?
Wissen anda i t-sersen ubesṭuḥ-nni daɣen
Yesɛa agelzim akked tqabcat caḍen-as
Teddez kullec s umehraz
Ur tettḥibbi ara ad tsexdem tamacint, txeddem s ifassen-is
Isuffeɣ-d adlis n tfizikt s teqbaylit
Drus n tektabin i d-yeffɣen s teqbaylit, nessaram ad ilint aṭas n wannect-a
Nessaram ad d-lalen daɣen widak ara iḍefṛen abrid-is
Nekk heddṛeɣ ar wudem, ur ttezziɣ ara i wawal
Teččuṛeḍ d ameɛɛen, wellah ar tɛeddaḍ deg temɣaṛt
Nettat tesɛa 6 n iseggasen, meɛna imeslayen-is am widak-nni n temɣaṛin
Ldi adli-is ar isebter wis xemsa utlatin
Ad d-qqlen meṛṛa ass n laṛebɛa ɣef tlata n tmeddit
Ad necḍeḥ arma neɛya deg tmeɣṛa-ines
Hḍeṛ akka i wi ur k-nessin ara, wama nekk ssneɣ-k!
Seḍsen-iyi-d imeslayen-im, ḥaca asfuǧeɣ i tesfuǧuɣeḍ
Ad ɛeddiɣ ad gneɣ, iseɛya-yi uxeddim ass-a
Ttemacent wallen-iw iman-nsent, deg iḍelli ma gneɣ ula d ddqiqa
